sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as Tenant-A client
    participant FD as Front Door + WAF
    participant AP as APIM
    participant LA as Language PII
    participant AG as Agent (LangChain)
    participant CS as Content Safety
    participant M as AOAI gpt-4o-customer RAI=strict-production-v1
    participant LAW as Log Analytics

    U->>FD: HTTPS POST /chat
    FD->>AP: forward (WAF passed)
    AP->>AP: validate-jwt (Entra)
    AP->>AP: rate-limit + quota
    AP->>AP: choose policy from JWT.role=customer
    AP->>AP: set-header x-policy-id=strict-production-v1
    AP->>LA: send-request: PII pre-scan
    LA-->>AP: redacted text + entities
    AP->>AP: validate header allow-list
    AP->>AG: forward + headers (x-policy-id, request-id)
    AG->>CS: analyze_text(input) + detect_jailbreak
    CS-->>AG: severities + jailbreak score
    Note over AG: BLOCK if severity >= Low (strict-production threshold)
    AG->>M: chat.completions ?rai-policy=strict-production-v1
    Note over M: L5 RAI thresholds, L6 default filters, L7 fin-strict blocklist (all run automatically)
    M-->>AG: response (or content_filter finish_reason)
    AG->>CS: analyze_text(output) + detect_groundedness + detect_protected_material
    CS-->>AG: pass / block + ungrounded spans
    AG->>LA: recognize_pii_entities(output)
    LA-->>AG: redact PII
    AG-->>AP: clean response
    AP-->>U: 200 OK
    par Telemetry (parallel)
      AP->>LAW: APIM logs
      AG->>LAW: OTel spans (x-policy-id, per-guard decision)
      M->>LAW: RAIContentFilterEvents
    end
